{{Infobox organization | name = PEPANZ | image = PEPANZ_logo.png | image_size = 300px | alt = | caption = | formation = <!-- use {{start date|YYYY|MM|DD|df=y}} --> | extinction = <!-- use {{end date and age|YYYY|MM|DD}} --> | headquarters = [[Wellington, New Zealand]] | location = | coords = <!-- {{coord|LAT|LON|display=inline,title}} --> | region = | services = | products = | methods = | fields = | membership = | membership_year = | board_of_directors = | key_people = Cameron Madgwick, CEO | staff = | staff_year = | volunteers = | volunteers_year = | mission = | website = {{URL|www.pepanz.com}} }}
The '''Petroleum Exploration and Production Association of New Zealand (PEPANZ)''' is an [[incorporated society]] based in [[Wellington]]. Its core focus is to promote the interests of [[petroleum]] producers and explorers in [[New Zealand]] which includes everything from policy through to education.<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.energyawards.co.nz/sponsors/pepanz| title=PEPANZ| publisher=NZ Energy Excellence Awards}}</ref>
Full members are those participating in a mining permit, participating in an exploration permit or a first time holder of any interest in exploration or production acreage. Full members include:<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.pepanz.com/about-us/our-members/| title=PEPANZ Member Directory|date=2017|publisher=PEPANZ|accessdate=27 August 2017}}</ref> * [[Anadarko Petroleum]] * [[Australian Worldwide Exploration]] * Beach Energy * [[Chevron Corporation]] * L&M Petroleum Ltd * New Zealand Oil and Gas * [[New Zealand Energy Corporation]] * [[OMV]] New Zealand Limited * [[Origin Energy]] (Lattice Energy) * [[Royal Dutch Shell]] (Shell (Petroleum Mining) Company Limited) * [[Statoil]] * [[TAG Oil]] * Tamarind Resources * [[Todd Corporation|Todd Petroleum Mining Company Limited]] * Westside Corporation * [[Woodside Petroleum]]
Associate members include service providers to the oil and gas industry in New Zealand (such as contractors, legal firms, engineers).
